-## Running the Application
-
-### Option 1: Docker Compose (recommended for demo)
-
-From the **repository root** (where `docker-compose.yml` lives):
-
-**1) TбәЎo `.env` (bбәҜt buб»ҷc cho Postgres):** sao chГ©p [.env.example](.env.example) вҶ’ `.env` vГ  giб»Ҝ hoбә·c Д‘б»•i `POSTGRES_PASSWORD`, `JWT_SECRET`, (tuб»і chб»Қn) `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID` / `MICROSOFT_CLIENT_ID`. Compose **khГҙng** cГІn mбәӯt khбә©u DB mбә·c Д‘б»Ӣnh trong file YAML.
-
-**Bash / Git Bash / macOS / Linux**
+## Quick start with Docker
 
-```bash
-cp .env.example .env
-# chб»үnh POSTGRES_PASSWORD / JWT_SECRET trong .env nбәҝu cбә§n
